info.description:
-----------------------------------
This Program Is made to browse Tv episoldes to download from the comfort of your desktop
---- IMPORTANT NOTE --------
You Should Have Torrent Client Download the video file.

---- KNOWN BUGS ------------
GUI unresponsive when loading search or new results.

[@] Some TV episodes are wont be able to download. 

---- INSTRUCTIONS ---------
after installing run the program by typing "freetele" without quotes
and browse the movie you want click download save the torrent file from the browser and open it with your torrent client
